FBIS4-60306 "drnes100_j_94025" FBIS-NES-94-100 Daily Report 24 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Wrapup of Reaction to al-Bid Secession Attempt Noted Wrapup of Reaction to al-Bid Secession Attempt Noted U.S. Reaction Noted JN2405064894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 0430 GMT 24 May 94 JN2405064894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] The U.S. State Department yesterday denounced al-Bid's secessionist announcement and called for political dialogue. According to AFP, State Department Spokesman Michael McCurry said the United States will not reply to al-Bid's Saturday announcement as it does not consider such basic issues can be decided while battles are continuing. The spokesman added that the immediate result of the secession announcement will be that of perpetuating battles and increasing the number of victims and the suffering of civilians.
